{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}],"role":"article","images":[{"type":"card","identifier":"gettingStarted-card.png"}],"title":"Getting Started with Sloths","roleHeading":"Article"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a sloth and assign personality traits and abilities to Sloth."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths are very complex creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise and rest."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every sloth has a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name","isActive":true},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":". You can optionally provide a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Create a Sloth","anchor":"Create-a-Sloth","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of "},{"code":"ice","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fire"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"wind"},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"code":"lightning","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", you can specify this at creation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:"}]},{"code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat","type":"heading","text":"Provide a Habitat","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","isActive":true},{"text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"]},{"anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth","text":"Exercise a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol and implementing the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Feed a Sloth","anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"]},{"text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth","type":"heading","anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a "},{"code":"Date","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:"}]},{"code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/SlothySample","doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"],"generated":true,"title":"Essentials"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/slothcreator\/gettingstarted"]}],"references":{"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Activity/perform(with:)":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Performs the work or sequence of actions for an activity.","type":"text"}],"title":"perform(with:)","required":true,"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/activity\/perform(with:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"perfor